      "title": "My latest Guardian Books cartoon ",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s640x960/ac6835a805c6354d5966f324924fd5324d19981b.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"827\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Panel 1 A repulsive voice rises from a hole in the wilderness &quot;Remember when books used to be fun? Before the box tickers and bean counters took over?&quot;  Panel 2 to 4 We follow the voice to an cave where an audience watches a fly/demon/monster at a lectern continue &quot;Publishers used to take risks: Books opened portals to hell, drove readers insane, or just moaned in a horrible way! When did you last see a broadsheet review of a book by a mad monk, an evil skeleton or a hobgoblin? My new imprint will challenge the publishing industry's pro-human bias with a ceaseless stream of foul books by malevolent authors.&quot;  Panel 5 The fly/demon/monster triumphantly finished &quot;Also, we'll be doing it entirely with AI!&quot; The ghouls of the audience shout &quot;Boo!&quot; &quot;Shame!&quot; &quot;Disgraceful!&quot; \" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s75x75_c1/7dee644e66bf21f060d5e979c98845d6c8cc09e4.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s100x200/a5843eb4c78c7c2b81079dcd9fae44060fd7f2ca.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s250x400/a6984b6c8c4a4b3158c233b5049b0a6f1ec91e9c.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s400x600/c3d92f36076f0a56b47fce9e8635ea9a6a0fe58e.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s500x750/d8438916c6d12220cc451b9935e68f306ad23a0f.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-88/s540x810/66c6630a01cdb34895f1cba3cd923358f555af8b.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84f5e8c7c45f3e4d2741fde956497654/6ed2113fe07b5ed0-