      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/815049208896815104",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/815049208896815104",
      "title": "Almost reading the greats. My latest Guardian Books cartoon.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s640x960/ab80afed0c62ad91e6be4ab813ae916d69c71c69.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"845\" data-orig-width=\"1500\" alt=\"Title: Almost reading the greats &#10;&#10;Panel one: &#10;A figure in a bookshop holds a thick book.&#10;Caption: I select the first volume of a vast biography of an important american. I appreciate its scholarship and heft. I put it down and pick up something short and funny.&#10;&#10;Panel two: &#10;A figure in a bookshop holds a thick book.&#10;Caption: I shiver as the new translation of a russian masterpiece transports Me to the awesome silence of a wintry night on the steode with the exquisite picture on its cover. &#10; &#10;Panel Three: &#10;A figure in a bookshop holds a thick book.&#10;Caption: I am moved close to tears as I hold the complete works of a great poet and marvel at the beauty and truth that I would find if I ever got round to reading it.&#10;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s75x75_c1/aa3245f42b36b5389fd0a3aa017f33a3af5fc9a5.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s100x200/4c4181b03fac7248ec384058aec30517d86e0aa6.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s250x400/df2bd2346a11009e88ba9c4d99cf281bd49e1d43.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s400x600/9d95e74ea15b7f782eeedaa1f38a9a99d5a7d6eb.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s500x750/78a55ecb102900414ed993ef189d2da13dc7bd68.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s540x810/6f2af89a9b646c70cb87f84d6820a35d6183f4a4.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/84afed683692537eb9d22b3f249857b7/99716d8e8304e765-ce/s640x960/ab80afed0c62ad91e6be4ab813ae916d69c71c69.jpg 640w,